Title:  Fields for Images

Seq:    5.11

Level:  3 - chapter

Class:  non-version

Timestamp: 20260409173053

Body:

These are fields that can be used to incorporate and display images (photos, diagrams, etc.)

Note that some of these fields are not unique field *types*, but simply special field *labels*.  I'll be sure to clarify these distinctions below. 
